law.history: Repealed 1958 Ky. Acts ch. 77, Art. 10, sec. 10-102, effective July 1, 1960. -- Amended 1948 Ky. Acts ch. 150, sec. 2. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 3720b-193.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Computation of time when day for doing act is Sunday or holiday.
